  <entry>
    <title>线性表</title>
    <link href="http://ccblogs.top/liner-tag.html"/>
    <id>http://ccblogs.top/liner-tag.html</id>
    <published>2019-04-24T17:10:46.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-04-28T07:18:28.543Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>线性表属于线性结构中逻辑结构中的线性结构。逻辑结构分为线性结构，几何结构，树形结构和图形结构四大结构。而线性表就属于线性结构。</p><blockquote><p>注意：本文使用C语言?</p></blockquote><h1 id="线性表"><a href="#线性表" class="headerlink" title="线性表"></a>线性表</h1><h2 id="概念"><a href="#概念" class="headerlink" title="概念"></a>概念</h2><p><strong>线性表:由零个或者多个数据元素组成的有序数列。</strong><br>线性表又包括：<strong>顺序存储和链式存储</strong><br>其中链式存储的地址不是连续的，它们是通过指针相连的。</p><h2 id="基本操作"><a href="#基本操作" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.建立空表</span><br><span class="line">2.定值查找</span><br><span class="line">3.定位查找</span><br><span class="line">4.指定位置插入</span><br><span class="line">5.指定位置删除</span><br><span class="line">6.输入线性表</span><br><span class="line">7.输出线性表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><hr><h1 id="顺序存储"><a href="#顺序存储" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储"></a>顺序存储</h1><p><strong>简单地说就是数组，寻找一块初始内存空间，然后在这块地址下的连续空间依次存放数据。通常又分为动态分配和静态分配，静态分配主要用栈，动态分配主要用堆(<del>记得防内存泄露</del>)</strong></p><blockquote><p>注意这块空间地址是连续滴?</p><ul><li><h2 id="顺序存储结构体定义"><a href="#顺序存储结构体定义" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储结构体定义"></a>顺序存储结构体定义</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">LNode</span> *<span class="title">list</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> position;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> MAX = <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">LNode</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> data[MAX];</span><br><span class="line">    position Last;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></blockquote><p>该结构定义需要注意三点:</p><ul><li>线性表的最大长度MAX</li><li>线性表的当前长度Last</li><li><p>线性表的起始内存位置</p></li><li><h2 id="顺序存储初始化"><a href="#顺序存储初始化" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储初始化"></a>顺序存储初始化</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="built_in">list</span> <span class="title">MakeEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">list</span> L;</span><br><span class="line">    L = (<span class="built_in">list</span>)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(struct LNode));<span class="comment">//为结构体申请空间</span></span><br><span class="line">    L-&gt;Last = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"Initial succeed\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> L;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>emmm,没什么好说的，看代?。</p><ul><li><h2 id="顺序存储的按值查找"><a href="#顺序存储的按值查找" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储的按值查找"></a>顺序存储的按值查找</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function">position <span class="title">Find</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">list</span> L,<span class="keyword">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    position i=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(i&lt;=L-&gt;Last<span class="number">-1</span>&amp;&amp;L-&gt;data[i]!=x)<span class="comment">//两个判断条件，一个是查找是否超过当前长度</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//一个是是否找到要找得值</span></span><br><span class="line">        i++;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(i&gt;L-&gt;Last)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> i+<span class="number">1</span>;<span class="comment">//这i+1...，看个人喜好当前长度得设置。</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>顺序存储呢，主要是按值查找，按位查找基本不需要写函数，数组嘛，怎么调用还是懂得吧?</p><blockquote><p>查找思路:从第一位开始遍历，遍历到要找得值，跳出循环，返回相应位置得值，历遍完当前长度都没有那个值，返回一个-1表示错误。</p><ul><li><h2 id="顺序存储的插入"><a href="#顺序存储的插入" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储的插入"></a>顺序存储的插入</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">Insert</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">list</span> L,<span class="keyword">int</span> x,position i)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(i&lt;<span class="number">0</span>||i&gt;L-&gt;Last)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//判断输入位置的正确性</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"position illegal\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(L-&gt;Last==MAX)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//判断表是否已满</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"Node max,cannot insert\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (position p = L-&gt;Last - <span class="number">1</span>; p &gt;= i<span class="number">-1</span>;p--)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//腾空要插入的位置</span></span><br><span class="line">        L-&gt;data[p + <span class="number">1</span>] = L-&gt;data[p];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    L-&gt;data[i<span class="number">-1</span>] = x;<span class="comment">//插入！?</span></span><br><span class="line">    L-&gt;Last++;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></blockquote><blockquote><p>插入的思路:先判断输入位置的正确性，再判断表是否满，如果满足上述条件，从要插入位置i开始，后面的数据往后挪一位</p></blockquote><p><strong>注意！挪动的时候要从最后一位开始挪，不然会造成数据丢失！！！！?</strong></p><ul><li><h2 id="顺序储存的删除"><a href="#顺序储存的删除" class="headerlink" title="顺序储存的删除"></a>顺序储存的删除</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">Delete</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">list</span> L,position i)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(i&lt;<span class="number">0</span>||i&gt;L-&gt;Last)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//跟插入一样判断插入位置正确性</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"position illegal\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (position p = i; p &lt; L-&gt;Last;p++)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//直接前挪覆盖数据，真霸道</span></span><br><span class="line">        L-&gt;data[p - <span class="number">1</span>] = L-&gt;data[p];</span><br><span class="line">    L-&gt;Last--;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p><strong>还是需要注意挪动方向性问题，这次的挪动是从前面往前挪的哦，跟插入操作的挪动有点不太一样?</strong></p><ul><li><h2 id="顺序存储的遍历输出"><a href="#顺序存储的遍历输出" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储的遍历输出"></a>顺序存储的遍历输出</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Show</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">list</span> L)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"Data:"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; L-&gt;Last;i++)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d "</span>, L-&gt;data[i]);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>这个还是比较简单的吧</p><ul><li><h2 id="顺序存储的输入"><a href="#顺序存储的输入" class="headerlink" title="顺序存储的输入"></a>顺序存储的输入</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Input</span><span class="params">(<span class="built_in">list</span> L,position num)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"Input data(total %d)\n"</span>, num);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; num;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;L-&gt;data[i]);</span><br><span class="line">        L-&gt;Last++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>这个也没什么好说的，跟输出一样的思路。</p><ul><li><h2 id="main函数"><a href="#main函数" class="headerlink" title="main函数"></a>main函数</h2>自己?，调用函数都不会?。</li></ul><hr><p>#链式存储</p><p>#未完待续。。。</p>]]></content>
    
