    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="最大子列和问题"><a href="#最大子列和问题" class="headerlink" title="最大子列和问题"></a>最大子列和问题</h1><h2 id="问题描述"><a href="#问题描述" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><blockquote><p>给定K个整数组成的序列{ N1, N2, …, NK}，“连续子列”被定义为{ N​i, Ni+1, …, Nj}，其 1≤i≤j≤K。“最大子列和”则被定义为所有连续子列元素的和中最大者。例如给定序列{ -2, 11, -4, 13, -5, -2 }，其连续子列{ 11, -4, 13 }有最大的20。现要求你编写程序，计算给定整数序列的最大子列和</p></blockquote><p>本题旨在测试各种不同的算法在各种数据情况下的表现。各组测试数据特点如下：</p><blockquote><ul><li>数据1：与样例等价，测试基本正确性；</li><li>数据2：102个随机整数；</li><li>数据3：103个随机整数；</li><li>数据4：104个随机整数；</li><li>数据5：105个随机整数；</li></ul></blockquote><h2 id="输入格式"><a href="#输入格式" class="headerlink" title="输入格式:"></a>输入格式:</h2><p>输入：1行给出正整数K (100000)；第2行给出K个整数，其间以空格分隔</p><h2 id="输出格式"><a href="#输出格式" class="headerlink" title="输出格式"></a>输出格式</h2><p>在一行中输出最大子列和。如果序列中所有整数皆为负数，则输0</p><h2 id="输入样例"><a href="#输入样例" class="headerlink" title="输入样例"></a>输入样例</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">-2 11 -4 13 -5 -2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="输出样例"><a href="#输出样例" class="headerlink" title="输出样例"></a>输出样例</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><hr><hr><h1 id="算法们："><a href="#算法们：" class="headerlink" title="算法们："></a>算法们：</h1><h2 id="暴力算法O-N-3"><a href="#暴力算法O-N-3" class="headerlink" title="暴力算法O(N^3)"></a>暴力算法O(N^3)</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">add1</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a[],<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> max=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> temp=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; k; i++) \\从第一个元素开始历</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> j = i; j &lt; k; j++)&#123; \\求和的最后一个元</span><br><span class="line">temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> n=i;n&lt;=j;n++)\\把前面两个<span class="keyword">for</span>确定的头尾元素夹着的子列和，加起来</span><br><span class="line">temp += a[n];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (temp &gt; max)</span><br><span class="line">max = temp;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> max;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这种算法的想法是最朴素，最容易的想到的。容易想到有容易想到的坏处，坏处是它的复杂度居然有O(N^3)那么大，太可怕了�?- -�?</p></blockquote><p><strong>这是我在PTA平台作业中提交时测的数据</strong><br><img src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ooeQQly1g29mfqf0m4j30yz0qd0ty.jpg" alt></p><p>还是蛮吓人的，毕竟我等这个结果也等了挺久- -<br>测试样例到五位数的时候直接超时了，实际上也不知道等到猴年马月，有兴趣的同学可以用C的tick测一下</p><hr><h2 id="稍微优化一下的算法O（N-2）："><a href="#稍微优化一下的算法O（N-2）：" class="headerlink" title="稍微优化一下的算法O（N^2）："></a>稍微优化一下的算法O（N^2）：</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">add2</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a[],<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> max = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; k; i++)\\从第一个元素开始历�?</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> j = i; j &lt; k; j++)在原来的基础上往后加一个元�?</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">temp += a[j];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (temp &gt; max)\\加一个比较一</span><br><span class="line">max = temp;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> max;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这种算法复杂度降了一个层次，实际上也不难想得到，比前面的算法稍微聪明点，少了许多重复的过程，重新利用了前面算好的数据</p></blockquote><p><strong>测试结果</strong><br><img src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ooeQQly1g29mh4iebgj30yz0qdt9y.jpg" alt></p><p>跟算法一对比，前两个数量级的测试实例相差不大，第三个开始耗时就相差一个数量级了。这第二个算法至少能把后面两个数量级的测试实例算出来，不过这耗时嘛，有点惨不忍睹。通常一个好的程序猿看到O（N^2,自然会想到能不能把这个算法优化成O（NlogN,这个算法呢，也就是我接下来介绍的算法�?</p><hr><h2 id="另外一种思想的算法（分而治之）（O-NlogN-�"><a href="#另外一种思想的算法（分而治之）（O-NlogN-�" class="headerlink" title="另外一种思想的算法（分而治之）（O(NlogN)�?:"></a>另外一种思想的算法（分而治之）（O(NlogN)�?:</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Max</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> left, <span class="keyword">int</span> right, <span class="keyword">int</span> middle)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="comment">//比较左边 右边 跨越中间的和 三者那个最</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (left &gt; right)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (right &gt; middle)          <span class="comment">//弱智的写法（是我本人了）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> left;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (middle &lt; left)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> left;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> middle;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (left &gt; middle)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> right;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (middle &lt; right)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> right;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> middle;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//return A &gt; B ? A &gt; C ? A : C : B &gt; C ? B : C;  简便的写法</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">div</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a[],<span class="keyword">int</span> left,<span class="keyword">int</span> right)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="comment">//分的算法，递归而治</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> leftsum, rightsum, middlesum; <span class="comment">//左边 右边 跨越中间的和 最大子列和</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> maxleft = <span class="number">0</span>, maxright = <span class="number">0</span>;  <span class="comment">//计算中间时左右的最大�?</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> templeft=<span class="number">0</span>, tempright=<span class="number">0</span>; <span class="comment">//计算中间最大值的临时�?</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> middle; <span class="comment">//中间的数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (left == right)  <span class="comment">//递归中止条件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (a[left] &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> a[left];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">middle = (left + right)/<span class="number">2</span>; <span class="comment">//算出中间的数�?</span></span><br><span class="line">leftsum = div(a, left, middle);  <span class="comment">//左边递归求解</span></span><br><span class="line">rightsum = div(a, middle + <span class="number">1</span>, right); <span class="comment">//右边递归求解</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = middle; i &gt;= left; i--) &#123;  <span class="comment">//中间的左边部分最大和</span></span><br><span class="line">templeft += a[i];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (templeft &gt; maxleft)</span><br><span class="line">maxleft = templeft;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = middle + <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;=right; i++) &#123; <span class="comment">//中间的右边部分最大和</span></span><br><span class="line">tempright += a[i];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (tempright &gt; maxright)</span><br><span class="line">maxright = tempright;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">middlesum = maxleft + maxright; <span class="comment">//中间最大和</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> Max(leftsum,rightsum,middlesum);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">add4</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a[], <span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> div(a, <span class="number">0</span>, k - <span class="number">1</span>); <span class="comment">//保持接口一</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>测试结果</strong></p><blockquote><p>这个算法理解起来不是很难，思想也比较简单，就是代码有点长，要用到递归，这需要对递归思想有一定理解才可以用，可以看到跟第二个算法相比最后一个测试数据有了质的提升！</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ooeQQly1g29mhl51opj30q10aft8y.jpg" alt><br><strong>举个例子</strong><br>          <img src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ooeQQly1g29mhtvge1j30id0catcf.jpg" alt></p><p>  有数 <code>4 -3 5 -2 -1 2 6 -2</code>，我们先从一分为二（递归）得到<code>4 -3 5 -2</code>(左边)，再一分为二（递归）得到<code>4 -3</code>,继续一分为二得到<code>4</code>和<code>-3</code>，然后<code>4</code>返回4，<code>-3</code>返回0，<code>4 -3</code>跨越中间得最大子列和1，于是比 4 0 1，<code>4 -3</code>返回得到4 ，同理<code>5 -2</code>返回得到5，在<code>4 -3 5 -2</code>中，往左右边扫描求出中间最大子列和6，再4 5 比较，<code>4 -3 5 -2</code>就返回得<strong>6</strong>，右边得<code>-1 2 6 -2</code>同理返回得到<strong>8</strong>,然后数列<code>4 -3 5 -2 -1 2 6 -2</code>从中间往左右扫，得到跨越中间得最大子列和<strong>11</strong>，与<strong>68</strong>比较，整个数列最后返11</p><p>  复杂度得计算如上图所</p><hr><h2 id="算是最优解的算法（在线处理法）（O（N））"><a href="#算是最优解的算法（在线处理法）（O（N））" class="headerlink" title="算是最优解的算法（在线处理法）（O（N））"></a>算是最优解的算法（在线处理法）（O（N））</h2><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">add3</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a[],<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> max = <span class="number">0</span>, temp=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; k; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">temp += a[i];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (temp &gt; max)</span><br><span class="line">max = temp;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (temp &lt; <span class="number">0</span>)<span class="comment">//小于0的子�? 全部抛弃</span></span><br><span class="line">temp = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> max;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>算法写起来时挺简单的吼，要想象它的正确性还是挺难的。从测试图可以看到其实提升还是有的，可能要列出第五个测试数据才能比较出与第三个算法的差别�?</p></blockquote><p><strong>测试结果</strong><br><img src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006ooeQQly1g29mi10uocj30q40aet8y.jpg" alt></p><p>这个算法是从右往左扫只扫一遍，扫一次加一次和，每次都判断和是否小0，如果是，整段抛弃，临时变量直接等于零，继续往后计算。实际上也不是很难，就是自己敲一遍才能更好地理解就是</p><h1 id="结语"><a href="#结语" class="headerlink" title="结语"></a>结语</h1><blockquote><p>第一篇博客写地还挺烂的吼<del>（自我感觉嘻嘻嘻）</del>，最大子列和也是学数据结构第一个接触到的多算法解决的问题，算法描述可能不是很周到，不过我还是会坚持写下去的<del>（虽然好像没什么人看（摊手））</del>，就这样啦，希望能帮到有需要的人~</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h1 id=&quot;最大子列和问题&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#最大子列和问题&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;最大子列和问题&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;最大子列和问题&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;问题描述&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#问题描述&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;问题描述&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;问题描述&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;给定K个整数组成的序列{ N1, N2, …, NK}，“连续子列”被定义为{ N​i, Ni+1, …, Nj}，其 1≤i≤j≤K。“最大子列和”则被定义为所有连续子列元素的和中最大者。例如给定序列{ -2, 11, -4, 13, -5, -2 }，其连续子列{ 11, -4, 13 }有最大的20。现要求你编写程序，计算给定整数序列的最大子列和&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本题旨在测试各种不同的算法在各种数据情况下的表现。各组测试数据特点如下：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;数据1：与样例等价，测试基本正确性；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;数据2：102个随机整数；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;数据3：103个随机整数；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;数据4：104个随机整数；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;数据5：105个随机整数；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;输入格式&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#输入格式&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;输入格式:&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;输入格式:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;输入：1行给出正整数K (100000)；第2行给出K个整数，其间以空格分隔&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;输出格式&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#输出格式&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;输出格式&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;输出格式&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在一行中输出最大子列和。如果序列中所有整数皆为负数，则输0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;输入样例&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#输入样例&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;输入样例&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;输入样例&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;-2 11 -4 13 -5 -2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;输出样例&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#输出样例&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;输出样例&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;输出样例&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
